node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Finance Father 👑 on August 09, 2021. May be an illustration of text that says 'I'm really worried about my future! Why?'.

Photo by Finance Father 👑 on August 09, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Well... because I have to do many things daily to make sure I'm successful! Work... Exercise... Learning... Social Life...'.
Photo by Finance Father 👑 on August 09, 2021. May be a cartoon of text that says 'But... sometimes I'm not able to do all those things... I just don't have the energy all the time...'.
Photo by Finance Father 👑 on August 09, 2021. May be an illustration of text that says 'And then I start thinking...'.
Photo by Finance Father 👑 on August 09, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'What will this mean for my future? Will I achieve anything? At this rate I will never achieve anything!'.
Photo by Finance Father 👑 on August 09, 2021. May be a cartoon of text that says 'Am I making the same mistakes as before? Am I doomed to the same fate?'.
Photo by Finance Father 👑 on August 09, 2021. May be a cartoon of text that says 'What's going to happen? Can you come back to the present?'.
Photo by Finance Father 👑 on August 09, 2021. May be an illustration of text that says 'Huh? It's easy to live in the future or the past!'.
Photo by Finance Father 👑 on August 09, 2021. May be a cartoon of text that says 'Yeah... But we can only improve in the present!'.
Photo by Finance Father 👑 on August 09, 2021. May be a cartoon of text that says 'Maybe focusing I guess on problems in so... so... this moment will help build a better life!'.
Photo by Finance Father 👑 on August 07, 2021. May be an image of 1 person and text that says 'Rakuten Rakuten SELF MADE. SELF PAID. SELF EDUCATED. DOUBLE TAP IF YOU'RE THE ONE'.
